            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25646213">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">上智与下愚不可移，此中智愚不可等同于智力。心性更多</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-04-08 10:20</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                上智与下愚不可移，此中智愚不可等同于智力。心性更多
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25646213/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2013-04-08 10:20
                </div>
              </div>
